org.usfirst.frc.team2077.video.interfaces

Interface VideoView

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    RenderedView
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    CompositeView, DefaultView

    public interface VideoView
    Displayable assembly of one or more RenderedView components. Each video feed in the view is associated with a VideoSource via a Rendering, which also defines how the source pixels are to be mapped into the view image via a RenderingProjection.

    Views are created by Main and are required to have a constructor taking parameter (String name), where name is its configuration property prefix.
